001package edu.cnm.deepdive.codebreaker.model;
002
003import com.google.gson.annotations.Expose;
004import com.google.gson.annotations.SerializedName;
005import java.time.Instant;
006import java.util.Date;
007
008public class Guess {
009
010  @SerializedName("key")
011  @Expose(serialize = false, deserialize = true)
012  private final String id;
013
014  @SerializedName("guessText")
015  @Expose
016  private final String content;
017
018  @Expose(serialize = false, deserialize = true)
019  private final int correct;
020
021  @Expose(serialize = false,deserialize = true)
022  private final int close;
023
024  @SerializedName("created")
025  @Expose(serialize = false, deserialize = true)
026  private final Date timestamp;
027
028  Guess(String content) {
029    this.content = content;
030    id = null;
031    correct = 0;
032    close = 0;
033    timestamp = null;
034  }
035
036  public String getId() {
037    return id;
038  }
039
040  public String getContent() {
041    return content;
042  }
043
044  public int getCorrect() {
045    return correct;
046  }
047
048  public int getClose() {
049    return close;
050  }
051
052  public Date getTimestamp() {
053    return timestamp;
054  }
055}
